title: Rainbow Six Siege - Official Street Fighter Bundle Trailer
description:
Rainbow Six Siege is introducing the Street Fighter Bundle to the hit tactical first-person shooter series developed by Ubisoft. Players can purchase two bundles featuring characters from the Street Fighter series with Ying as Chun-Li and Grim as Ryu. The Street Fighter Bundles for Rainbow Six Siege is available now for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox, Amazon Luna, and PC.

#RainbowSixSiege #StreetFighter #ChunLi #Ryu

title: Rick and Morty Is About To Get Back To The Big Story
description:
Rick and Morty is already halfway through Season 7 but Co-Creator Dan Harmon and Executive Producer Scott Marder tell us the show is about to return to the big story that’s been cooking in the background all this time. Will Rick catch up with Rick Prime? Will their ensuing conflict destroy the multiverse? Harmon and Marder dive into the messed-up psyche of Rick C-137 plus how they balance writing the fun Rick and Morty one-off episodes with the episodes dealing with that larger story.

#RickAndMorty
